---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
import Hero from '../components/sections/Hero.astro'
import Content from '../components/sections/Content.astro'
import Checklist from '../components/Checklist.astro'
import ChecklistItem from '../components/ChecklistItem.astro'
import PricingCard from '../components/PricingCard.astro'
import Socials from '../content/socials.astro'
import Faq from '../content/Faq.astro'
import FaqItem from '../content/FaqItem.astro'
import Timed from '../components/Timed.astro'
import Button from '../components/Button.astro'
import Pacman from '../components/Pacman.astro'
import { start_registration } from '../data/reg/dates.json'
---

<Base>
  <Hero headline="Prepare your quest">
    <p>Discover ticket options, accommodation packages, and ways to support Flüüfff.</p>
    <Timed start={start_registration} class="mt-4">
      <Button label="Register" to="https://registration.fluufff.org" />
    </Timed>
    <Pacman class="mt-8 hidden md:block" />
  </Hero>
  <Content headline="Accommodation" bg="primary" wider class="pricing_content">
    <p>Choose where you’ll respawn: stay at the convention venue from Wednesday to Sunday.</p>
    <p>
      <strong>The room prices listed below are for the full room and do not include the Convention Ticket.</strong>
    </p>
    <Checklist row primary>
      <ChecklistItem>Personal badge with lanyard</ChecklistItem>
      <ChecklistItem>Hotel stay for the duration of the convention</ChecklistItem>
      <ChecklistItem>Access to general amenities</ChecklistItem>
      <ChecklistItem>Breakfast included!</ChecklistItem>
    </Checklist>
    <div class="pricing">
      <PricingCard
        image={import('../assets/images/venue/classic_double.jpg')}
        title="Classic Double / Twin"
        price="575"
        pricePer="per room"
        extra={['Early Arrival: + €144 incl. VAT', 'Late Departure: + €144 incl. VAT']}
      >
        <p>2 pers. max - 28 m² / 308 sq ft</p>
        <p>Shared classic room for two people, with either a double bed, or separate beds.</p>
      </PricingCard>
      <PricingCard
        image={import('../assets/images/venue/superior_double.jpg')}
        title="Superior Double"
        price="615"
        pricePer="per room"
        extra={['Early Arrival: + €154 incl. VAT', 'Late Departure: + €154 incl. VAT']}
      >
        <p>2 pers. max - 28 m² / 308 sq ft</p>
        <p>Shared room with a double bed.</p>
      </PricingCard>
      <PricingCard
        image={import('../assets/images/venue/privilege_room.jpg')}
        title="Privilege Room with a View (3p)"
        price="825"
        pricePer="per room"
        extra={['Early Arrival: + €206 incl. VAT', 'Late Departure: + €206 incl. VAT']}
      >
        <p>3 pers. max - 36 m² / 387 sq ft</p>
        <p>Spacious shared room with a kingsize bed and a pull-out sofa with Parkview</p>
      </PricingCard>
      <PricingCard
        image={import('../assets/images/venue/superior_studio.jpg')}
        title="Superior Studio (3p)"
        price="915"
        pricePer="per room"
        extra={['Early Arrival: + €229 incl. VAT', 'Late Departure: + €229 incl. VAT']}
      >
        <p>3 pers. max - 36 m² / 387 sq ft'</p>
        <p>Spacious, comfortable studio with kingsize bed, sofa bed, lounge and kitchen.</p>
      </PricingCard>
    </div>
    <p class="pricing_details">
      Room price covers the full room. One person books and pays the total amount and arranges roommates independently.
      Con fee not included in prices.<br />
      <!--<a href="/venue">Check out this page for more information on the venue.</a>-->
    </p>
  </Content>
  <Content headline="Convention Tickets" class="pricing_content" wider>
    <p>Choose your play mode: join for a day, the weekend, or the full convention.</p>
    <div class="pricing">
      <PricingCard
        color="primary"
        title="Day ticket"
        price="40-50"
        pricePer="per person*"
        checklist={[
          'Full access for a day to all convention events, programming, and general amenities',
          'Personal badge with lanyard'
        ]}
      />
      <PricingCard
        color="primary"
        title="Weekend ticket"
        price="70"
        pricePer="per person"
        checklist={[
          'Full access to all convention events, programming, and general amenities from Saturday until Sunday',
          'Personal badge with lanyard'
        ]}
      />
      <PricingCard
        color="dark"
        title="All-Days Pass"
        price="175"
        pricePer="per person"
        checklist={[
          'Full access to all convention events, programming, and general amenities from Wednesday until Sunday',
          'Personal badge with lanyard'
        ]}
      />
    </div>
    <p class="pricing_details">
      *Day tickets vary by day: Wednesday €40, Thursday–Saturday €50. Sunday is only available with an all-day pass or
      Weekend ticket. Accommodation is not included in these prices. Note: There will be no refunds for registration
      fees.
    </p>
  </Content>
  <Content headline="Sponsorships" class="pricing_content" bg="primary-dark" wider>
    <p>Contribute to the growth of Flüüfff and get recognized as a valued supporter of our community.</p>
    <div class="pricing">
      <PricingCard
        image={import('../assets/images/illustrations/sponsors/builder.png')}
        imageContain
        color="primary"
        title="Builder"
        price="40"
        description="Provide support that helps us cover the essential building blocks of the convention."
        checklist={[
          'Your own convention T-shirt',
          'Mention in the conbook',
          'Special Builder badge',
          'Our eternal gratitude'
        ]}
      />
      <PricingCard
        image={import('../assets/images/illustrations/sponsors/architect.png')}
        imageContain
        color="primary"
        title="Architect"
        price="90"
        description="Contribute at a higher level and help shape the experience for our community."
        checklist={[
          'An exclusive Sponsor T-shirt',
          'Mention in the conbook',
          'Special Architect badge',
          'Our eternal gratitude',
          'Exclusive goodie bag',
          'Your name listed on the closing ceremony slides'
        ]}
      />
      <PricingCard
        image={import('../assets/images/illustrations/sponsors/patron.png')}
        imageContain
        color="dark"
        title="Patron"
        price="200"
        checklist={[
          'An exclusive Sponsor T-shirt',
          'Mention in the conbook',
          'Special Patron badge',
          'Our eternal gratitude',
          'Exclusive goodie bag',
          'Your name listed on the closing ceremony slides',
          'A special mention on our website',
          "An exclusive, personalised, SFW art piece in this year's theme by Ni3ls",
          'A personal, handwritten, thank-you note from the Chairdragon'
        ]}
      >
        <p>Offer significant support and play a key role in sustaining and growing Flüüfff.</p>
        <p><strong>Limited to 10 Patrons</strong></p>
      </PricingCard>
    </div>
  </Content>
  <Socials />
  <Faq>
    <FaqItem question="Do I need a ticket to attend Flüüfff?">
      Yes. All attendees need a valid ticket to access the convention. You can choose between day tickets, a weekend
      ticket, an all-days pass.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="What is the difference between Accommodation and Convention tickets?">
      <p>Convention tickets (day, weekend, or all-days) give you access to the event.</p>
      <p>
        Accommodation covers your stay at the hotel from Wednesday to Sunday and does not include access to the
        convention.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you would like to both attend the event and stay at the venue, you will need to book both a convention ticket
        and accommodation.
      </p>
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="How do residential room bookings work?">
      Residential rooms are booked per room, not per person. One attendee books and pays for the room, and roommates can
      arrange payment among themselves. This allows groups of friends to easily share a room together during the
      convention.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="Can I share a room with friends?">
      Yes! Residential rooms are meant to be shared depending on the room type you choose. The person who books the room
      can decide who stays in the room with them.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="Can I upgrade or change my ticket later?">
      In many cases upgrades may be possible depending on availability. If you would like to upgrade your ticket or
      sponsorship level, please contact our support team and we’ll be happy to assist you.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="Can I get a refund if I can’t attend?">
      Registration fees are non-refundable. If you can no longer attend, please contact our support team and we will try
      to help you find the best possible solution.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="Do I need to be a gamer or have a fursuit to join?">
      Not at all! Flüüfff welcomes everyone who enjoys creativity, community, and the furry fandom. Whether you come in
      full fursuit, casual cosplay, or just as yourself, you are welcome.
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="How do I stay updated about Flüüfff?">
      The best way to stay up to date is by following our social media channels and joining our Telegram community.
      Important announcements will also always be posted on the website.
    </FaqItem>
  </Faq>
</Base>

<style lang="scss" is:global>
  .content .pricing {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 22px;
    margin: 48px 0;

    // @media (max-width: 1200px) and (min-width: 601px) {
    //   display: grid;
    //   align-items: stretch;
    //   grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    //   flex-direction: column;
    //   align-items: center;

    //   > :nth-child(odd) {
    //     justify-self: end;
    //   }
    // }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;

      .pricing-card {
        width: auto;
        min-width: 250px;
      }
    }
  }

  .content .pricing_details {
    max-width: 480px;
  }
</style>
